 Our results\ndemonstrate the power of galaxy data to place tight constraints on CIP, and\nmotivate works to understand better the impact of data systematics, as well as\nto determine theory priors for $b_\\sigma$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Feb 2023 18:59:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-06"}
